1
00:00:05,380 --> 00:00:06,990
What in the heck happened?

2
00:00:06,990 --> 00:00:09,320
I was shocked when I found you on the floor.

3
00:00:09,320 --> 00:00:12,160
I got dizzy all of a sudden
and my feet got tangled.

4
00:00:12,160 --> 00:00:14,660
I'm sorry that I made you worry.

5
00:00:14,660 --> 00:00:16,400
Maybe you're slightly anemic.

6
00:00:16,400 --> 00:00:18,100
What do you want to do?
Do you want to go see a doctor?

7
00:00:18,100 --> 00:00:21,690
No, I'll be all right. I think I just need some rest.

8
00:00:22,770 --> 00:00:24,870
The remedial classes have started.

9
00:00:24,870 --> 00:00:28,170
Missing one day isn't going to
make any difference.

10
00:00:28,170 --> 00:00:29,180
You should rest today.

11
00:00:29,180 --> 00:00:30,180
Okay.

12
00:00:30,180 --> 00:00:31,910
What about your job today?

13
00:00:31,910 --> 00:00:33,500
I'll take the day off.

