I went to the shrine with Yukito.

21
00:00:51,260 --> 00:00:54,030
You shouldn't look in someone else's diary.

22
00:00:54,830 --> 00:00:57,390
Don't you have anything else to write about?

23
00:00:58,640 --> 00:01:00,340
I think I'm doing a good job, though...

24
00:01:00,340 --> 00:01:04,410
Well, to be blunt, you don't have
any talent for diary-writing.

25
00:01:04,410 --> 00:01:07,780
So from now on, instead of writing about
what you did, write about what you want to do.

26
00:01:07,780 --> 00:01:09,850
But then, it's not a diary.

27
00:01:09,850 --> 00:01:11,550
Yes it is,

28
00:01:11,550 --> 00:01:14,020
because I'll make all of those things come true.

29
00:01:17,120 --> 00:01:20,020
I want to go to the ocean... with you, Yukito.

30
00:01:20,830 --> 00:01:24,160
We've never gone down to the beach together.

31
00:01:24,160 --> 00:01:28,200
I want to dig in the sand and
pick up pretty seashells.

32
00:01:28,200 --> 00:01:31,430
You can see the ocean anytime, can't you?

33
00:01:32,170 --> 00:01:33,470
Gao!

34
00:01:33,470 --> 00:01:34,710
Ouch!

35
00:01:34,710 --> 00:01:36,110
Fine.

36
00:01:36,640 --> 00:01:40,170
I'll go to the beach with you.

37
00:01:41,110 --> 00:01:41,980
Yeah!

38
00:01:43,080 --> 00:01:46,850
We watched the vapor trails

39
00:01:46,850 --> 00:01:50,690
As they disappeared

40
00:01:51,020 --> 00:01:54,690
We ran from the blinding light

41
00:01:54,690 --> 00:02:04,090
In vexation we let go

42
00:02:04,770 --> 00:02:12,070
There are still places she cannot reach

43
00:02:12,750 --> 00:02:19,320
She gazes with wistful eyes

44
00:02:19,320 --> 00:02:27,660
Children walk along the tracks in summer

45
00:02:27,660 --> 00:02:34,000
In both hands, their wish to take wing

46
00:02:34,430 --> 00:02:42,170
We chased and chased vanishing vapor trails

47
00:02:42,170 --> 00:02:49,050
Since the day we climbed over that hill

48
00:02:49,050 --> 00:02:51,120
Unfailingly

49
00:02:51,120 --> 00:02:53,820
And just like we have always

50
00:02:53,820 --> 00:02:57,260
Stood straight and tall

51
00:02:57,790 --> 00:03:06,400
We will stay as strong as the god of the sea

52
00:03:06,400 --> 00:03:10,990
Surely

53
00:03:23,920 --> 00:03:27,520
The girl said she wanted to see the ocean.

54
00:03:27,520 --> 00:03:30,820
But I couldn't take her.

55
00:03:35,690 --> 00:03:39,150
Episode 7

56
00:03:39,870 --> 00:03:42,070
Misuzu fainted?

57
00:03:42,070 --> 00:03:45,140
Yeah, she hasn't been feeling well all day.

58
00:03:45,140 --> 00:03:48,470
She's resting in her room.
Could you go check on her?

59
00:03:48,470 --> 00:03:52,650
If she sees my drunken face,
she'll feel even worse.

60
00:03:52,650 --> 00:03:56,640
Hey, I brought some sushi.
Let's enjoy it together.

61
00:04:01,650 --> 00:04:03,790
That really hurt, you know.

62
00:04:03,790 --> 00:04:06,330
Why did you take Misuzu in?

63
00:04:06,330 --> 00:04:07,590
Huh?

64
00:04:07,590 --> 00:04:10,330
Why did you take Misuzu in?

65
00:04:10,330 --> 00:04:13,590
Oh, so she told you about that...

66
00:04:15,270 --> 00:04:18,540
I didn't choose to take her in. I was forced into it.

67
00:04:18,540 --> 00:04:20,810
I said I didn't want her.

68
00:04:20,810 --> 00:04:23,910
That's why she can't lean on you.

69
00:04:23,910 --> 00:04:27,350
Think about it! For her, you're her only parent!

70
00:04:27,350 --> 00:04:30,980
She has an episode whenever
she gets friendly with someone.

71
00:04:31,720 --> 00:04:34,490
She and I never got emotionally close.

72
00:04:34,490 --> 00:04:36,950
That's why this is working.

73
00:04:37,090 --> 00:04:38,890
What is a family, I wonder...

74
00:04:38,890 --> 00:04:43,300
I don't know because I'm not her real mom.

75
00:04:43,300 --> 00:04:46,130
Ugh... This one isn't good.

76
00:04:53,070 --> 00:04:58,980
The girl dreams. The first one is about the sky.

77
00:04:58,980 --> 00:05:02,280
The dreams keep going back in time.

78
00:05:02,280 --> 00:05:06,290
The dreams plague her.

79
00:05:06,290 --> 00:05:09,360
She starts to feel pain for no reason.

80
